      "text": "Compliance with chapter required. No for-hire carrier or private carrier shall operate any motor vehicle for the transportation of persons or property, or both, on any public highway in this state except in accordance with the provisions of this chapter. [Formerly 767.040; 1997 c.275 35] ECONOMIC AND SAFETY REGULATION (Applicability)",
